room_title: Escape room "Pirate Cove Plunder" by Katy Rock Escape in Windsor
review: We had a great time! Very fun and challenging! We finished it!... but with 5 minutes added because we almost had it and were having fun. Great time!

room_title: Escape room "Pirate Cove Plunder" by Katy Rock Escape in Windsor
review: We went here for our friend's birthday. It was suprisingly pretty awesome. We had so much fun in the pirate room and will be going back to do the egyptian room.
